    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even want to make something \"smaller.\" i don't want to perform anymore. it feels like i've already finished my part. like the story is done and i'm just stuck in the epilogue for no reason. does it ever feel like once the purpose is gone, there's nothing left to justify the struggle?",
